# Tiny End-to-End Example

## Document

```text
The capital of France is Paris.
The capital of Germany is Berlin.
The capital of Italy is Rome.
```

### Chunks

```text
Chunk 1:
The capital of France is Paris.

Chunk 2:
The capital of Germany is Berlin.

Chunk 3:
The capital of Italy is Rome.
```

### User Question

```text
What is the capital of Germany?
```

### Retrieved Chunk

```text
The capital of Germany is Berlin.
```

### Final Answer

```text
Berlin is the capital of Germany.
```

