# Why RAG is Powerful

| Without RAG                 | With RAG                      |
| --------------------------- | ----------------------------- |
| Uses only training data     | Uses your documents           |
| Can hallucinate             | More accurate                 |
| Cannot access private files | Can answer from private files |
| Knowledge may be outdated   | Uses latest uploaded data     |

