# Summary

RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) works in three simple stages:

```text
Documents
     ↓
Retrieve Relevant Information
     ↓
Generate Accurate Answer
```

Think of RAG as:

```text
Google Search
      +
ChatGPT
      =
RAG
```

The system first finds the correct information and then lets the AI answer using that information.
